rti.template:
To,
The Designated Officer
{officeName}

Subject: Application for Information under Right to Information Act 2009

Sir/Madam,

Under the Right to Information Act 2009, I request the following information:

Applicant Details:
Name: {applicantName}
Address: {address}
Phone: {phone}
Email: {email}
National ID: {nid}

Information Requested:
{informationRequested}

Time Period: {timeframe}
Purpose: {purpose}

I am willing to pay the prescribed fee for obtaining this information as per Section 6 of the RTI Act 2009. Please provide the information within 20 working days as mandated by Section 9 of the Act.

If any part of this information is not available or cannot be provided, please inform me in writing with proper justification as required under the Act.

Thank you for your cooperation.

Yours faithfully,

{applicantName}
Date: {currentDate}
Phone: {phone}
NID: {nid}

Note: This application is submitted under the Right to Information Act 2009. Fee enclosed: 2 Taka per page (as applicable)
